END AS "SourceChannel", m."Status", NULL AS "MessageType", m."MessageContent", COALESCE(m."ProviderMessageId", m."MessageId") AS "ProviderMessageId", m."ErrorMessage", m."CreatedAt", m."SentAt", NULL AS "DeliveredAt"
